&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EBME Admin Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has risen for an enthusiastic and committed individual to join our EBME department at Darent Valley Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful post holder will be the first point of contact in the reception area and monitor the electronic helpdesk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for updating various databases, book in and our deliveries and help with other admin tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires excellent interpersonal skills as well as a flexible approach, good time management and organizational skills, attention to detail and excellent verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameMiora CrowJob titleHead of EBMEEmail addressmoira.crow@nhs.netTelephone number8210Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Welcome to contact for an informal chat and vist&lt;/p&gt;
